    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Crowns that appear at the four corners or surmounting the peaks of  baldachins. These may be portable or permanently fixed, and may be ornamented in various ways, often with ostrich feathers.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
